> unUsable eXpression Manager

Just a "Travail d'Initiative Personnelle Encadr√©" project :3

Syntax
------

Define a rule
=============

defrule <name2>
    <expr1> into <expr2>
end

defrule <name1>
    | <expr1> into <expr2>
    ...
    | <exprn> into <exprn>
end

Define an eXpression
====================

defex <name> <expr> end

Apply a rule
============

apply <rule name> <expr name>

Print eXpression
================

puts <expr name>

Examples
--------

Peano Numbers:

defrule add
    | s(x) + y into s(x + y)
    | s(0 + x) into s(x)
    | 0 + s(x) into s(x)
end

defex threePlusFour
    s(s(s(0))) + s(s(s(s(0))))
end

apply add threePlusFour
apply add threePlusFour
apply add threePlusFour
apply add threePlusFour
apply add threePlusFour

puts threePlusFour

Logic:

defrule modusPonens
    true(p) /\ true(p -> q) into true(q)
end

defrule induction
    true(p(n0)) /\ true((p(n) -> p(n+1)) into true(p(n))
end
